{"tid":2484524,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美軍神盾艦長翹腳近距監控遼寧艦  日前曾指揮迫近長江口","createTime":"2021-04-11T15:36:55.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-14T07:28:52.000Z","uid":184679,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"ea74cc26839600fccb562dc88c7c2fce9aa288fa","tid":2484524,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T15:36:55.000Z","msg":"美國海軍公布柏克級（Arleigh Burke-class）神盾驅逐艦「馬斯廷號」（USS Mustin DDG 89）4月4日在菲律賓海近距監控解放軍航空母艦遼寧號的照片。該艦長甚至將脚翹起。<br />\n<br />\n但此圖不久疑陸續遭删除，但截至記者發稿為止，仍有照片可搜尋到。<br />\n<br />\n前海軍新江艦長呂禮詩解讀照片表示，美艦艦長和副長一起目視監控距離不到4000碼的解放軍「遼寧號」航空母艦。<br />\n<br />\n呂禮詩解讀表示，照片中的CO是艦長，當然能在駕駛台大搖大擺的坐著翹著腳的、也就只有艦長；旁邊則是副艦長。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，中國「南海戰略態勢感知計畫」（SCSPI）平台3日凌晨在微博發文，船舶自動識別系統（AIS）顯示馬斯廷艦出現在東海長江口海域，「針對性明顯」；這更是間接的說明了，原來美軍更早偵獲遼寧號編隊的動態，早已派遣馬斯廷號一路併航監控，從東海穿越宮古水道、向東進入菲律賓海。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.worldjournal.com/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/wj/realtime/2021/04/11/12064107.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=800&amp;exp=3600&amp;q=75&amp;nt=1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.worldjournal.com%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2Fwj%2Frealtime%2F2021%2F04%2F11%2F12064107.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D800%26exp%3D3600%26q%3D75%26nt%3D1&h=35b7a248&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5381144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121469%2F5381144&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8KwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=e227df0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5381144</a>"},{"pid":"74583d21f4bab9386827d1f92ce5f97e449392e2","tid":2484524,"uid":39209,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T15:40:54.000Z","msg":"遼寧艦直頭幫美軍護航啦。"},{"pid":"aceaeb37c65958dfd7a018071e0b9c60c42ad257","tid":2484524,"uid":54125,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T15:43:18.000Z","m