F%2Fwww.worldjournal.com%2Fwj%2Fstory%2F121469%2F5381144&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8KwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=e227df0d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.worldjournal.com/wj/story/121469/5381144</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:04:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覺得唔係艦長<br />\n<br />\n應該係水手清潔完甲板蛇王緊，企係到個個其實等緊位坐<br />\n影相個個覺得佢地好gay，影低張相諗住返艙笑鳩佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n艦長應該係自己個靚艙訓緊覺，副艦長就係艙到數緊仲有幾多年先可坐正。<br />\n大副係室內駕駛台抱怨緊，跟隻支那航母好撚悶，已經跟左2日1夜<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，艦長幾時先肯上黎頂更<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sorry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8564eddd514cc7d515eb1cfb517cf17cfee751ef","tid":2484524,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:06:19.000Z","msg":"中共艦想投誠咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e664422f14bc6a5741cc4a5a5867b609eea0874","tid":2484524,"uid":313615,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-11T16:07:31.000Z","msg":"中共海軍的CV 16遼寧號<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/遼寧號航空母艦\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%81%BC%E5%AF%A7%E8%99%9F%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%AF%8D%E8%89%A6&d=WFG5iCHEkkmufTvr7zh8KwsTF5hDypdTwPi8eTnvKzQ%3D&h=8a3328d1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/遼寧號航空母艦</a><br />\n<br />\n跟蹤的軍艦是DDG-89馬廷斯號，是第三十九艘阿利伯克級宙斯盾艦，隸屬第七艦隊，母港橫須賀<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/馬斯廷號驅逐艦_\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%BB%B7%E8%99%9F%E9%A9%85%E9%80%90